official_title: A joint resolution prohibiting the proposed sales of certain missiles to Saudi Arabia.

summary.text: Prohibits the issuance of a letter of offer with respect to specified proposed sales of Sidewinder, Stinger, and Harpoon missiles and services to Saudi Arabia, as described in the April 8, 1986, certifications from the President to the Congress under the Arms Export Control Act.
